title: Idina Menzel / Broken Rib & Vocal Health
description: Sean and Dr. Wali discuss cell phone neck strain and Sean’s disastrous waffle making attempt. Idina Menzel tells the tale of breaking a rib while performing Wicked and then being carted off to the hospital in full green witch makeup. She also shares the vital task of protecting her voice.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
